

Using the "f500.csv" dataset, print the first 5 rows and first 3 columns of this dataset using pandas.
Output Format
                    company  rank  revenues
0                   Walmart     1    485873
1                State Grid     2    315199
....



Solution

## Open and read data file as specified in the question
## Print the required output in given format
import pandas as pd
f500 = pd.read_csv('f500.csv')
print(f500.iloc [:5, :3])
